folder: Burnett Street & Avenue U, Brooklyn, NY
text:
(1) Gerritsen Creek, south of Ave. U, and east of Burnett Street, showing the Gerritsen grist mill, and also showing a view to the south west. 1922. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, showing a close-up of the mill and the spillway. 1922. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3) The same, another view. August 1923. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(4) The same, showing at the right, a section of the mansion. In the foreground is a section of Marsh Street. This view will eventually be land, and will be enclosed in Marine park. September 1928. Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
